articles.author: Mike Wall
articles.title: Blue Origin scrubs 1st New Glenn rocket launch due to technical issue - Space.com
articles.description: It's unclear when the powerful new rocket will make its debut.
articles.content:
We'll have to wait a bit longer to see Blue Origin's New Glenn rocket lift off for the first time.
